text: Muhammad Akmal Nor Hasrin (born 15 July 1995) is a male Malaysian recurve archer. He competed in the archery competition at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:Malaysian male archers Category:Living people Category:1995 births Category:Malaysian people of Malay descent Category:Malaysian Muslims Category:Archers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic archers of Malaysia Category:Sportspeople from Kuala Lumpur Category:Archers at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Malaysia
